DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Chicago Public Library\\nCost: free\\nAges: 0-60 mo
 nths\\nCategory: Storytime\\n\\nCardz For Kidz is a non-profit that aims t
 o uplift the spirits of people around the world who might need extra encou
 ragement. We send handmade cards from "artists" from around the world to k
 ids in the hospital\, foster homes\, orphanages\, seniors and people in th
 e armed forces. At this event we sort through the cards that we have recei
 ved\, count them and package the cards to send to our different partners. 
 We welcome all ages to come and help us uplift spirits! For adults and fam
 ilies. How to Atte\\n\\nMore info: https://chipublib.bibliocommons.com/eve
 nts/69ea3f5bbd5c392c76461e37
