CATEGORIES:museum,science,family,all_audiences
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Field Museum - Events\\nCost: Included with admissi
 on\\nAges: All ages\\nCategory: General\\n\\nMeet Lazaro W. Vinola Lopez\,
  Postdoctoral Research Scientist\, and Ken Marks\, Fossil Preparator\, as 
 they showcase recently unearthed fossils from a 7-million-year-old site in
  the Caribbean. Learn about the unexpected animals scientists have discove
 red during their excavations\; explore the differences between these fossi
 ls and animals already known to be from the Caribbean islands\; and see ho
 w these discoveries are impacting what scientists know about the fauna on 
 the islands.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.fieldmuseum.org/our-events/meet-a
 -scientist/meet-a-scientist-caribbean-fossils
LOCATION:Field Museum\, 1400 S Lake Shore Dr\, Chicago\, IL 60605
URL:https://www.fieldmuseum.org/our-events/meet-a-scientist/meet-a-scienti
 st-caribbean-fossils
