SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:museum,science,family,all_audiences
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Field Museum - Events\\nCost: Included with admissi
 on\\nAges: All ages\\nCategory: General\\n\\nView extraterrestrial materia
 ls from the Field Museum's collection and explore how scientists use them 
 to learn more about our cosmic origin story. Meet Philipp R. Heck\, Sr Dir
 ector of Research and Robert A. Pritzker Curator\, and hear how elements a
 re formed in the stars and shuttled in stardust through space to form the 
 solar system. Examine meteorites and stardust up close as you consider the
  deep time connection these objects provide us.\\n\\nMore info: https://ww
 w.fieldmuseum.org/our-events/meet-a-scientist/meet-a-scientist-our-cosmic-
 origins
LOCATION:Field Museum\, 1400 S Lake Shore Dr\, Chicago\, IL 60605
URL:https://www.fieldmuseum.org/our-events/meet-a-scientist/meet-a-scienti
 st-our-cosmic-origins
