DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Field Museum - Events\\nCost: Ticket required\\nAge
 s: All ages\\nCategory: General\\n\\nJoin us for an evening celebrating th
 e grand opening of the Pokémon Fossil Museum at the Field Museum! Receive
  exclusive\, after-hours access to the exhibit and embark on your own foss
 il adventure through the exhibit halls of the Field Museum. You’ll want 
 to catch all this event has to offer\, including demonstrations by our tea
 m of scientists\, hands-on activities\, crafts\, and of course\, plenty of
  fossils! Guests must register in advance and will receive a timed-entry t
 icket for the Pokémon Fossil Museum at check-in. Access to all other muse
 um exhibitions\, including the Crown Family PlayLab and After the Age of D
 inosaurs \, are included with admission. All sales are final.\\n\\nMore in
 fo: https://www.fieldmuseum.org/our-events/field-family-nights/family-nigh
 t-featuring-the-pokemon-fossil-museum
LOCATION:Field Museum\, 1400 S Lake Shore Dr\, Chicago\, IL 60605
URL:https://www.fieldmuseum.org/our-events/field-family-nights/family-nigh
 t-featuring-the-pokemon-fossil-museum
