 stern Europe to stave off everyday ailments\, as well as protect themselve
 s from curses. Presenters include Emma Turner-Trujillo\, Assistant Regist
 rar\, Anthropology Collections\; Christina Thompson\, Anthropology Collect
 ions\, and Registration Assistant Jada Whiterock\, Mellon Registration & C
 ultural Engagement Specialist.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.fieldmuseum.org
 /our-events/meet-a-scientist/jewish-botany-plant-medicine-and-magic-in-the
 -jewish-diaspora
